Huawei :huawei:
Колеги из другой команды ищут специалиста в офис на Владыкино (в будущем переезд на Смоленскую).
*От себя*: для всех сотрудников есть ежегодный бонус (до нескольких окладов), компенсация падения :rub: к :heavy_dollar_sign:(раз в год), возможен аналог опционов (после 1-2 лет работы, говорят сравним с бонусом).
*По вакансии*: ищут от джунов, до синьоров, всего несколько позиций (head count); вопросы по вакансии к Александре Клименко (почта снизу).

Описание от hr:
AI specialist (Video Processing)

*Key Responsibilities:*
• Developing next generation of video coding technologies essentially based on CNN;
• Designing network structure and optimizing its performance based on video compression criteria;
• Optimizing complexity of CNN based video coding solution.

*Requirements:*
• Ms degree or PhD in Signal Processing, or Computer Science, or similar;
• 3+ years’ experience in CNN (Tensorflow, Pytorch, Keras) in the field of image and video processing, profound Python knowledge;
• 2+ years’ experience in digital signal processing or/and coding is a plus;
• Be interested in video compression research or other video processing technology;
• Experience in variational autoencoders is a big bonus;
• Good oral and written communication, interpersonal and cooperation skills, good English.

*Salary frame* ~120k~350k (depending on experience)

P.S. we also can consider students without industrial experience, but have strong theoretical knowledge and the willing to dig into video processing technology.
If you are interested, please send your english CV to <mailto:klimenko.aleksandra@huawei.com|klimenko.aleksandra@huawei.com>

